@mylahill Watching you grow into a strong, independent young woman has been an absolute joy. We are beyond proud of you on the extraordinary and significant milestone of turning 21 today. Your intellect, curiosity & passion are just some of the characteristics that are uniquely you. As you continue onward in pursuing and protecting your dreams, don't ever forget that you are unconditionally loved and adored by mom & dad.. #happybirthdaymyla #happy21st #mylahill 🎉🎂🥳🎈🎊🎁

@realgranthill & @reallaelhill & I had so much fun visiting the @empirestatebldg on Memorial Day to watch the sunset from the 103rd floor terrace. Definitely a must if you're ever in NYC.. empirestatebuildingobservatory #empirestatebuilding #kingkongbroadway

I'm still soaring after our trip to South Africa where @realtamiaworld had 4 sold out shows last week in Pretoria, Cape Town & Durban. To witness 12,000 people every night sing every word to every song of hers, was powerful, and almost spiritual in a way. Needless to say, she represented as my daughters and I watched in awe as @realtamiaworld shared her gift with the beautiful people in the Rainbow Nation 🇿🇦#southafrica #tamia
